 largest one alcoa technical center is located east of its pittsburgh headquarters at alcoa center pennsylvania the tech center is as large as some college campuses has its own zip code and maintains an extensive intellectual and physical resource for innovation alcoas extensive safety program continuously improves safety at the tech center after paul oneill became alcoa ceo in  alcoa became one of the safest companies in the world despite the aluminum industrys inherent risks alcoa makes cans for the soft drink industry alcoa plans to close offices in richmond virginia nashville tennessee and chicago in popular cultureedit alcoa is portrayed as the main sponsor of the cbs  program see it now in george clooneys academy award–nominated film good night and good luck see alsoedit companies portal book aluminium alumina list of alumina refineries alcoa world alumina and chemicals alcoa tennessee alcoa power generating inc list of aluminum smelters  alcoa aluminum advertisement referencesedit  a b c d e f alcoa corp  annual report form k filing date mar   secgov retrieved april      statista  httpswwwstatistacomstatisticslargestaluminumcompaniesworldwide retrieved   missing or empty title help  a b almy mom coa inc  annual report form k filing date feb   pdf secdatabasecom retrieved june     alcoa form k current report filing date may   pdf secdatabasecom retrieved jan     alcoa form sc tota filing date jul   secdatabasecom retrieved jan     a b alcoa completes corporate split aluminum insider november   retrieved april     a b press the associated  alcoa moving headquarters back to pittsburgh wtae retrieved    hachezleroy florence  aluminum industry a heritage for europe pdf proceedings ticcih congress archived pdf from the original on  november  retrieved    rosenbaum david ira  market dominance how firms gain hold or lose it and the impact on economic performance praeger publishers via greenwood publishing group p  isbn  archived from the original on  november  retrie